    <omv:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/okn/o/sd#OntologyEngineering"/>
    <omv:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology xml:lang="en">Iterative ontology engineering methodology based on FAIR principles, competency questions, semantic alignments, and ontology reuse.</omv:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology>
    <prov:wasGeneratedBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#OntologyEngineeringWorkflow"/>
    <prov:wasGeneratedBy xml:lang="en">Developed as part of the EMSO ERIC Data Management Service Group activities</prov:wasGeneratedBy>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Co-construction with domain experts and iterative alignment with reference ontologies</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="no">Samskaping med fagpersoner og iterativ tilpasning til referanseontologier</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="fr">Co-construction avec des experts métier et alignement itératif avec des ontologies de référence</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="ro">Co-construcție cu experți din domeniu și aliniere iterativă cu ontologii de referință</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="it">Co-costruzione con esperti di dominio e allineamento iterativo con ontologie di riferimento</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">Co-construcción con expertos del dominio y alineación iterativa con ontologías de referencia</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="pt">Co-construção com especialistas no domínio e alinhamento iterativo com ontologias de referência</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">Συνεκπόνηση με ειδικούς του τομέα και επαναληπτική ευθυγράμμιση με πρότυπες οντολογίες</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">Οντολογία που περιγράφει τις σχέσεις μεταξύ περιφερειακών υποδομών, τοποθεσιών, πλατφορμών, ερευνητικών υποδομών, οργανισμών, αποστολών και των υπευθύνων σε κάθε επίπεδο.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Ontology describing the relationships between Regional Facilities, Sites, Platforms, Research Infrastructures, Organisations, Cruises, and the persons in charge of each level.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">Ontología que describe las relaciones entre instalaciones regionales, emplazamientos, plataformas, infraestructuras de investigación, organizaciones, cruceros y las personas responsables de cada nivel.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="fr">Ontologie décrivant les relations entre les nœuds régionaux, les sites, les plateformes, les infrastructures de recherche, les organisations, les campagnes à la mer et les personnes responsables à chaque niveau.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="it">Ontologia che descrive le relazioni tra strutture regionali, siti, piattaforme, infrastrutture di ricerca, organizzazioni, crociere e i responsabili di ciascun livello.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="no">Ontologi som beskriver forholdet mellom regionale fasiliteter, steder, plattformer, forskningsinfrastrukturer, organisasjoner, cruiser og de ansvarlige på hvert nivå.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="pt">Ontologia que descreve as relações entre instalações regionais, locais, plataformas, infraestruturas de investigação, organizações, cruzeiros e os responsáveis por cada nível.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="ro">Ontologie care descrie relațiile dintre facilitățile regionale, siturile, platformele, infrastructurile de cercetare, organizațiile, croazierele și persoanele responsabile la fiecare nivel.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">OSO includes selected semantic alignments with SWEET concepts to improve interoperability with Earth and environmental science vocabularies.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="fr">OSO inclut des alignements sémantiques ciblés avec des concepts SWEET afin d'améliorer l'interopérabilité avec les vocabulaires des sciences de la Terre et de l'environnement.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">OSO incluye alineaciones semánticas seleccionadas con conceptos de SWEET para mejorar la interoperabilidad con vocabularios de ciencias de la Tierra y del medio ambiente.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="it">OSO include allineamenti semantici selezionati con concetti SWEET per migliorare l'interoperabilità con i vocabolari delle scienze della Terra e dell'ambiente.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="pt">A OSO inclui alinhamentos semânticos selecionados com conceitos SWEET para melhorar a interoperabilidade com vocabulários das ciências da Terra e do ambiente.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="no">OSO inkluderer utvalgte semantiske tilpasninger til SWEET-begreper for å forbedre interoperabiliteten med vokabularer innen jord- og miljøvitenskap.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="ro">OSO include alinieri semantice selectate cu concepte SWEET pentru a îmbunătăți interoperabilitatea cu vocabularele din științele Pământului și ale mediului.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">Το OSO περιλαμβάνει επιλεγμένες σημασιολογικές αντιστοιχίσεις με έννοιες SWEET, ώστε να βελτιωθεί η διαλειτουργικότητα με λεξιλόγια των επιστημών της Γης και του περιβάλλοντος.</rdfs:comment>
