    <dcterms:provenance xml:lang="en">The ontology was developed and maintained using Protégé 5.6.9, VSCodium 1.121.03429 and RDFLib 7.6.0, version-controlled and published through GitHub. Versioning follows Semantic Versioning (SemVer) and commit history follows the Conventional Commits specification. Ontology metadata are reviewed and updated, and ontology statistics are recomputed for each release.</dcterms:provenance>
    <dcterms:provenance xml:lang="fr">L'ontologie a été développée et maintenue à l'aide de Protégé 5.6.9, VSCodium 1.121.03429 et RDFLib 7.6.0, versionnée et publiée via GitHub. La gestion des versions suit Semantic Versioning (SemVer) et l'historique des commits respecte la spécification Conventional Commits. Les métadonnées de l'ontologie sont vérifiées et mises à jour, et les statistiques de l'ontologie sont recalculées à chaque nouvelle version.</dcterms:provenance>
    <dcterms:provenance xml:lang="es">La ontología fue desarrollada y mantenida utilizando Protégé 5.6.9, VSCodium 1.121.03429 y RDFLib 7.6.0, versionada y publicada mediante GitHub. El versionado sigue Semantic Versioning (SemVer) y el historial de commits cumple la especificación Conventional Commits. Los metadatos de la ontología se revisan y actualizan, y las estadísticas de la ontología se recalculan en cada nueva versión.</dcterms:provenance>
    <dcterms:provenance xml:lang="it">L'ontologia è stata sviluppata e mantenuta utilizzando Protégé 5.6.9, VSCodium 1.121.03429 e RDFLib 7.6.0, versionata e pubblicata tramite GitHub. Il versionamento segue Semantic Versioning (SemVer) e la cronologia dei commit rispetta la specifica Conventional Commits. I metadati dell'ontologia vengono verificati e aggiornati, e le statistiche dell'ontologia vengono ricalcolate a ogni nuova versione.</dcterms:provenance>
    <dcterms:provenance xml:lang="pt">A ontologia foi desenvolvida e mantida utilizando o Protégé 5.6.9, o VSCodium 1.121.03429 e o RDFLib 7.6.0, versionada e publicada através do GitHub. O versionamento segue o Semantic Versioning (SemVer) e o histórico de commits respeita a especificação Conventional Commits. Os metadados da ontologia são revistos e atualizados, e as estatísticas da ontologia são recalculadas a cada nova versão.</dcterms:provenance>
    <dcterms:provenance xml:lang="no">Ontologien ble utviklet og vedlikeholdt med Protégé 5.6.9, VSCodium 1.121.03429 og RDFLib 7.6.0, versjonskontrollert og publisert gjennom GitHub. Versjoneringen følger Semantic Versioning (SemVer), og commit-historikken følger spesifikasjonen Conventional Commits. Ontologiens metadata blir gjennomgått og oppdatert, og ontologistatistikken blir beregnet på nytt for hver nye versjon.</dcterms:provenance>
    <dcterms:provenance xml:lang="ro">Ontologia a fost dezvoltată și întreținută utilizând Protégé 5.6.9, VSCodium 1.121.03429 și RDFLib 7.6.0, gestionată prin controlul versiunilor și publicată prin GitHub. Versionarea urmează Semantic Versioning (SemVer), iar istoricul commit-urilor respectă specificația Conventional Commits. Metadatele ontologiei sunt revizuite și actualizate, iar statisticile ontologiei sunt recalculate pentru fiecare nouă versiune.</dcterms:provenance>
    <dcterms:provenance xml:lang="el">Η οντολογία αναπτύχθηκε και συντηρείται με χρήση των Protégé 5.6.9, VSCodium 1.121.03429 και RDFLib 7.6.0, τελεί υπό έλεγχο εκδόσεων και δημοσιεύεται μέσω GitHub. Η διαχείριση εκδόσεων ακολουθεί το Semantic Versioning (SemVer), ενώ το ιστορικό των commits συμμορφώνεται με την προδιαγραφή Conventional Commits. Τα μεταδεδομένα της οντολογίας ελέγχονται και ενημερώνονται, ενώ τα στατιστικά της οντολογίας επανυπολογίζονται σε κάθε νέα έκδοση.</dcterms:provenance>
