  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#EMSO-Italia">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchInfrastructure"/>
    <OSO:hasCountry rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Italy"/>
    <OSO:isManagedBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#INGV"/>
    <schema1:url rdf:resource="https://www.ingv.it/monitoraggio-e-infrastrutture/emso"/>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://www.ingv.it/monitoraggio-e-infrastrutture/emso"/>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://emso.eu/"/>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://www.ogs.it/it/european-multidisciplinary-seafloor-and-water-column-observatory-emso-eric"/>
    <foaf:depiction rdf:resource="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/emso-eric/oso-ontology/main/images/emso_italia.png"/>
    <schema1:logo rdf:resource="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/emso-eric/oso-ontology/main/images/emso_italia.png"/>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="en">marine observatory</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="en">deep-sea observatory</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="en">ocean observation</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="en">research infrastructure</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="en">Mediterranean Sea</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="en">EMSO</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="it">osservatorio marino</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="it">osservazione oceanica</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="it">infrastruttura di ricerca</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="it">Mar Mediterraneo</dcat:keyword>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="el">Το EMSO-Italia αποτελεί την ιταλική συμβολή στην ευρωπαϊκή ερευνητική υποδομή EMSO, συντονίζοντας πολυεπιστημονικά θαλάσσια παρατηρητήρια και δραστηριότητες μακροχρόνιας ωκεανογραφικής παρατήρησης στη Μεσόγειο Θάλασσα.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="en">EMSO-Italia is the Italian contribution to the EMSO European research infrastructure, coordinating multidisciplinary marine observatories and long-term ocean observation activities in the Mediterranean Sea.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="es">EMSO-Italia es la contribución italiana a la infraestructura europea de investigación EMSO, coordinando observatorios marinos multidisciplinares y actividades de observación oceánica a largo plazo en el mar Mediterráneo.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="fr">EMSO-Italia est la contribution italienne à l’infrastructure de recherche européenne EMSO, coordonnant des observatoires marins multidisciplinaires et des activités d’observation océanique à long terme en mer Méditerranée.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="it">EMSO-Italia è il contributo italiano all'infrastruttura di ricerca europea EMSO, coordinando osservatori marini multidisciplinari e attività di osservazione oceanica a lungo termine nel Mar Mediterraneo.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="no">EMSO-Italia er det italienske bidraget til den europeiske forskningsinfrastrukturen EMSO, og koordinerer tverrfaglige marine observatorier og langsiktige havobservasjonsaktiviteter i Middelhavet.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="pt">EMSO-Italia é a contribuição italiana para a infraestrutura europeia de investigação EMSO, coordenando observatórios marinhos multidisciplinares e atividades de observação oceânica de longo prazo no Mar Mediterrâneo.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="ro">EMSO-Italia reprezintă contribuția italiană la infrastructura europeană de cercetare EMSO, coordonând observatoare marine multidisciplinare și activități de observare oceanografică pe termen lung în Marea Mediterană.</dcterms:description>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="el">Η ιταλική συνιστώσα του EMSO ERIC, αφιερωμένη στη μακροχρόνια πολυεπιστημονική παρατήρηση του θαλάσσιου πυθμένα και της υδάτινης στήλης στην περιοχή της Μεσογείου.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">The Italian component of EMSO ERIC, supporting long-term multidisciplinary observation of the seafloor and water column in the Mediterranean region.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="es">La componente italiana de EMSO ERIC, dedicada a la observación multidisciplinaria a largo plazo del fondo marino y de la columna de agua en la región mediterránea.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">La composante italienne d’EMSO ERIC, dédiée à l’observation multidisciplinaire à long terme du fond marin et de la colonne d’eau dans la région méditerranéenne.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="it">La componente italiana di EMSO ERIC, dedicata all’osservazione multidisciplinare a lungo termine del fondale marino e della colonna d’acqua nella regione mediterranea.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="no">Den italienske delen av EMSO ERIC, dedikert til langsiktig tverrfaglig observasjon av havbunnen og vannsøylen i Middelhavsregionen.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="pt">A componente italiana do EMSO ERIC, dedicada à observação multidisciplinar de longo prazo do fundo marinho e da coluna de água na região mediterrânica.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="ro">Componenta italiană a EMSO ERIC, dedicată observației multidisciplinare pe termen lung a fundului marin și a coloanei de apă din regiunea mediteraneană.</skos:definition>
