    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="fr">Site test de Molène</skos:altLabel>
    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="br">Enez Molenez</skos:altLabel>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Coastal cabled marine observation site located in the Iroise Sea and operated as an EMSO-France test site between 2012 and 2017.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">Site côtier câblé d’observation marine situé en mer d’Iroise et exploité comme site test d’EMSO-France entre 2012 et 2017.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="br">Lec’h sellout ouzh ar mor kevreet dre gebl e Mor Iroise, implijet evel lec’h arnodiñ ha heuliañ ar vevliesseurted hag ar biomassezhioù gant EMSO-France etre 2012 ha 2017.</skos:definition>
  </rdf:Description>
