    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">An open-source web application for querying, exploring and visualizing SPARQL endpoints.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">Une application web open source permettant d'interroger, d'explorer et de visualiser des endpoints SPARQL.</skos:definition>
