    <owl:inverseOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#isManagedBy"/>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Links an organisation to the research infrastructure it manages or coordinates.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="fr">Lie une organisation à l’infrastructure de recherche qu’elle gère ou coordonne.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">Relaciona una organización con la infraestructura de investigación que gestiona o coordina.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="it">Collega un'organizzazione all'infrastruttura di ricerca che gestisce o coordina.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="pt">Liga uma organização à infraestrutura de investigação que gere ou coordena.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="no">Knytter en organisasjon til forskningsinfrastrukturen den administrerer eller koordinerer.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="ro">Leagă o organizație de infrastructura de cercetare pe care o gestionează sau coordonează.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">Συνδέει έναν οργανισμό με την ερευνητική υποδομή που διαχειρίζεται ή συντονίζει.</rdfs:comment>
