    <skos:definition xml:lang="ro">Leagă o persoană de identificatorul său ORCID (Open Researcher and Contributor ID).</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="el">Συνδέει ένα πρόσωπο με το αναγνωριστικό ORCID (Open Researcher and Contributor ID).</skos:definition>
