    <skos:definition xml:lang="el">Πρώην Γενικός Διευθυντής του EMSO ERIC και θαλάσσιος γεωφυσικός που συμμετέχει σε ευρωπαϊκές θαλάσσιες ερευνητικές υποδομές.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Former Director General of EMSO ERIC and marine geophysicist involved in European marine research infrastructures.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="es">Antiguo Director General de EMSO ERIC y geofísico marino implicado en infraestructuras europeas de investigación marina.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">Ancien directeur général d’EMSO ERIC et géophysicien marin impliqué dans les infrastructures européennes de recherche marine.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="it">Ex direttore generale di EMSO ERIC e geofisico marino coinvolto nelle infrastrutture europee di ricerca marina.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="no">Tidligere generaldirektør for EMSO ERIC og marin geofysiker involvert i europeiske marine forskningsinfrastrukturer.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="pt">Antigo Diretor-Geral do EMSO ERIC e geofísico marinho envolvido em infraestruturas europeias de investigação marinha.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="ro">Fost director general al EMSO ERIC și geofizician marin implicat în infrastructurile europene de cercetare marină.</skos:definition>
  </rdf:Description>
