    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">A Regional Facility of EMSO-PT located on the Condor Seamount, west-southwest of Faial Island in the Azores.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">Une infrastructure régionale d’EMSO-PT située sur le mont sous-marin Condor, à l’ouest-sud-ouest de l’île de Faial aux Açores.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="pt">Uma infraestrutura regional do EMSO-PT localizada no monte submarino Condor, a oeste-sudoeste da ilha do Faial, nos Açores.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="no">Et regionalt anlegg i EMSO-PT lokalisert ved Condor-sjøfjellet, vest-sørvest for Faial-øya på Azorene.</skos:definition>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#MOMARSAT">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SeriesOfOceanographicCampaigns"/>
    <dcterms:identifier>10.18142/130</dcterms:identifier>
    <dcterms:isReferencedBy rdf:resource="https://doi.org/10.18142/130"/>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://doi.org/10.18142/130"/>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://campagnes.flotteoceanographique.fr/series/130/"/>
    <schema1:url rdf:resource="https://campagnes.flotteoceanographique.fr/series/130/"/>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">MOMAR is the acronym for MOnitoring the Mid Atlantic Ridge.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="fr">MOMAR est l’acronyme de MOnitoring the Mid Atlantic Ridge.</rdfs:comment>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="el">Σειρά ωκεανογραφικών αποστολών αφιερωμένων στην παρακολούθηση των υδροθερμικών περιβαλλόντων της Μεσο-Ατλαντικής Ράχης.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="en">Series of oceanographic campaigns dedicated to the monitoring of the Mid-Atlantic Ridge hydrothermal environments.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="es">Serie de campañas oceanográficas dedicadas al seguimiento de los entornos hidrotermales de la dorsal mesoatlántica.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="fr">Série de campagnes océanographiques dédiée au suivi des environnements hydrothermaux de la dorsale médio-atlantique.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="it">Serie di campagne oceanografiche dedicate al monitoraggio degli ambienti idrotermali della dorsale medio-atlantica.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="no">Serie av oseanografiske kampanjer dedikert til overvåking av hydrotermale miljøer langs den midtatlantiske ryggen.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="pt">Série de campanhas oceanográficas dedicadas à monitorização dos ambientes hidrotermais da dorsal meso-atlântica.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="ro">Serie de campanii oceanografice dedicate monitorizării mediilor hidrotermale ale dorsalei medio-atlantice.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:spatial rdf:resource="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mid-Atlantic_Ridge"/>
    <dcterms:spatial rdf:resource="http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Atlantic_Ocean"/>
