    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Subsurface mooring platform deployed in the southern Svinøy section of the Norwegian Sea for long-term ocean monitoring.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">Plateforme de mouillage subsurface déployée dans la partie sud de Svinøy en mer de Norvège pour le suivi océanique à long terme.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="no">Subsurface-mooringplattform utplassert i den sørlige delen av Svinøy i Norskehavet for langsiktig havovervåking.</skos:definition>
    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="en">Svinoy South mooring</skos:altLabel>
