    <skos:note xml:lang="en">Located within the Lucky Strike hydrothermal vent protected marine area (OSPAR MPA, WDPA 555557074).</skos:note>
    <skos:note xml:lang="fr">Situé dans l’aire marine protégée Lucky Strike hydrothermal vent (AMP OSPAR, WDPA 555557074).</skos:note>
    <skos:note xml:lang="pt">Localizado na área marinha protegida Lucky Strike hydrothermal vent (AMP OSPAR, WDPA 555557074).</skos:note>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Hydrothermal observation site located on the Mid-Atlantic Ridge near the Azores and operated within EMSO-France.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">Site d’observation hydrothermale situé sur la dorsale médio-atlantique à proximité des Açores et exploité dans le cadre d’EMSO-France.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="pt">Sítio de observação hidrotermal localizado na Dorsal Mesoatlântica, perto dos Açores, e operado no âmbito do EMSO-France.</skos:definition>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchInfrastructure">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"/>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Organization"/>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/cerif/vocab/Organisation"/>
    <metadata:prefixIRI>OSO:ResearchInfrastructure</metadata:prefixIRI>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">Μια ερευνητική υποδομή μπορεί να συγκεντρώνει μία ή περισσότερες Περιφερειακές Εγκαταστάσεις.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">A research infrastructure may bring together one or more Regional Facilities.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">Una infraestructura de investigación puede reunir una o más Instalaciones Regionales.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="fr">Une infrastructure de recherche peut regrouper une ou plusieurs installations régionales.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="it">Una infrastruttura di ricerca può riunire una o più Strutture Regionali.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="no">En forskningsinfrastruktur kan samle én eller flere regionale fasiliteter.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="pt">Uma infraestrutura de investigação pode reunir uma ou mais Instalações Regionais.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="ro">O infrastructură de cercetare poate reuni una sau mai multe facilități regionale.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="el">Ερευνητική Υποδομή</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Research Infrastructure</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="es">Infraestructura de Investigación</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="fr">Infrastructure de recherche</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="it">Infrastruttura di Ricerca</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="no">Forskningsinfrastruktur</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="pt">Infraestrutura de Investigação</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="ro">Infrastructură de cercetare</rdfs:label>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">The following definition for RI from Article 2 (6) of the Regulation (EU) No 1291/2013 of 11 December 2013: `Establishing Horizon 2020 - the Framework Programme for Research and Innovation (2014-2020)` applies: “RI are facilities, resources and services that are used by the research communities to conduct research and foster innovation in their fields. They include: major scientific equipment (or sets of instruments), knowledge-based resources such as collections, archives and scientific data, e-infrastructures, such as data and computing systems and communication networks and any other tools that are essential to achieve excellence in research and innovation.” Accordingly, RI are implemented along different organisational models, including central sources and laboratories for experiments and measurement sessions, coordination and management of geographically distributed observatories or laboratories, remotely accessible resources for computing, data banks, physical sample repositories, surveys and longitudinal studies.</skos:definition>
    <skos:note xml:lang="el">ΕΥ</skos:note>
    <skos:note xml:lang="en">RI</skos:note>
    <skos:note xml:lang="es">IIdI</skos:note>
    <skos:note xml:lang="fr">IR</skos:note>
    <skos:note xml:lang="it">IR</skos:note>
    <skos:note xml:lang="no">FI</skos:note>
    <skos:note xml:lang="pt">II</skos:note>
    <skos:note xml:lang="ro">IC</skos:note>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="el">Ερευνητική Υποδομή</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Research Infrastructure</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="es">Infraestructura de Investigación</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="fr">Infrastructure de recherche</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="it">Infrastruttura di Ricerca</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="no">Forskningsinfrastruktur</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="pt">Infraestrutura de Investigação</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="ro">Infrastructură de cercetare</skos:prefLabel>
  </rdf:Description>
