    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="en">Horizon Europe INFRA programme</skos:altLabel>
    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="fr">Programme Horizon Europe INFRA</skos:altLabel>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">European Horizon Europe project supporting long-term ocean observations and environmental sustainability within EMSO ERIC.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">Projet européen Horizon Europe soutenant les observations océaniques à long terme et la durabilité environnementale au sein d’EMSO ERIC.</skos:definition>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="el">Το EMSO EVOLVE είναι ένα ευρωπαϊκό έργο που υποστηρίζει τις μακροπρόθεσμες ωκεάνιες παρατηρήσεις και την περιβαλλοντική βιωσιμότητα στο πλαίσιο του EMSO ERIC.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="en">EMSO EVOLVE is a European project supporting long-term ocean observations and environmental sustainability within the EMSO ERIC framework.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="es">EMSO EVOLVE es un proyecto europeo que apoya las observaciones oceánicas a largo plazo y la sostenibilidad medioambiental en el marco de EMSO ERIC.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="fr">EMSO EVOLVE est un projet européen soutenant les observations océaniques à long terme et la durabilité environnementale dans le cadre d’EMSO ERIC.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="it">EMSO EVOLVE è un progetto europeo che sostiene le osservazioni oceaniche a lungo termine e la sostenibilità ambientale nel quadro di EMSO ERIC.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="no">EMSO EVOLVE er et europeisk prosjekt som støtter langsiktige havobservasjoner og miljømessig bærekraft innenfor rammen av EMSO ERIC.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="pt">EMSO EVOLVE é um projeto europeu que apoia observações oceânicas de longo prazo e a sustentabilidade ambiental no quadro do EMSO ERIC.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="ro">EMSO EVOLVE este un proiect european care sprijină observațiile oceanice pe termen lung și sustenabilitate de mediu în cadrul EMSO ERIC.</dcterms:description>
  </rdf:Description>
