    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="ro">Această proprietate leagă o organizație de identificatorul său ROR (Research Organization Registry).</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">Αυτή η ιδιότητα συνδέει έναν Οργανισμό με το αναγνωριστικό ROR (Research Organization Registry).</rdfs:comment>
