    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="el">Αξιολογητής FAIR για οντολογίες</skos:altLabel>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="en">FAIR assessment</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="en">Ontology FAIRness</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="en">semantic artefacts</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="en">FAIR Principles</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="fr">évaluation FAIR</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="fr">ontologies</dcat:keyword>
    <dcat:keyword xml:lang="fr">artefacts sémantiques</dcat:keyword>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Ontology FAIRness Evaluator (O'FAIRe) is a metadata-based automatic FAIRness assessment methodology and web application for ontologies and semantic artefacts. It evaluates semantic artefacts using 61 assessment questions derived from the O'FAIRe methodology and produces FAIR scores aligned with the FAIR principles.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">Ontology FAIRness Evaluator (O'FAIRe) est une méthodologie et une application web d’évaluation automatique de la FAIRness, fondées sur les métadonnées, pour les ontologies et les artefacts sémantiques. Elle évalue les artefacts sémantiques à l’aide de 61 questions d’évaluation issues de la méthodologie O'FAIRe et produit des scores FAIR conformes aux principes FAIR.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="es">Ontology FAIRness Evaluator (O'FAIRe) es una metodología y una aplicación web de evaluación automática de la FAIRness, basadas en metadatos, para ontologías y artefactos semánticos. Evalúa los artefactos semánticos mediante 61 preguntas de evaluación derivadas de la metodología O'FAIRe y genera puntuaciones FAIR alineadas con los principios FAIR.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="it">Ontology FAIRness Evaluator (O'FAIRe) è una metodologia e un'applicazione web per la valutazione automatica della FAIRness, basata sui metadati, per ontologie e artefatti semantici. Valuta gli artefatti semantici mediante 61 domande di valutazione derivate dalla metodologia O'FAIRe e produce punteggi FAIR conformi ai principi FAIR.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="pt">Ontology FAIRness Evaluator (O'FAIRe) é uma metodologia e uma aplicação web de avaliação automática da FAIRness, baseada em metadados, para ontologias e artefactos semânticos. Avalia os artefactos semânticos utilizando 61 questões de avaliação derivadas da metodologia O'FAIRe e produz pontuações FAIR alinhadas com os princípios FAIR.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="ro">Ontology FAIRness Evaluator (O'FAIRe) este o metodologie și o aplicație web de evaluare automată a FAIRness, bazate pe metadate, pentru ontologii și artefacte semantice. Evaluează artefactele semantice folosind 61 de întrebări de evaluare derivate din metodologia O'FAIRe și produce scoruri FAIR aliniate la principiile FAIR.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="no">Ontology FAIRness Evaluator (O'FAIRe) er en metadatabasert metodikk og webapplikasjon for automatisk vurdering av FAIRness for ontologier og semantiske artefakter. Den evaluerer semantiske artefakter ved hjelp av 61 vurderingsspørsmål basert på O'FAIRe-metodikken og produserer FAIR-poeng i samsvar med FAIR-prinsippene.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="el">Το Ontology FAIRness Evaluator (O'FAIRe) είναι μια μεθοδολογία και διαδικτυακή εφαρμογή αυτόματης αξιολόγησης της FAIRness, βασισμένη σε μεταδεδομένα, για οντολογίες και σημασιολογικά τεχνουργήματα. Αξιολογεί τα σημασιολογικά τεχνουργήματα χρησιμοποιώντας 61 ερωτήσεις αξιολόγησης που προέρχονται από τη μεθοδολογία O'FAIRe και παράγει βαθμολογίες FAIR ευθυγραμμισμένες με τις αρχές FAIR.</skos:definition>
    <schema1:url rdf:resource="https://services.agroportal.lirmm.fr/ofaire/"/>
    <foaf:depiction rdf:resource="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7379183/159973558-3ef49b10-f363-4172-9565-c3cc8a347881.png"/>
    <schema1:publisher rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#LIRMM"/>
    <dcterms:type xml:lang="en">FAIR assessment tool</dcterms:type>
    <dcterms:type xml:lang="fr">Outil d’évaluation FAIR</dcterms:type>
    <dcterms:type xml:lang="es">Herramienta de evaluación FAIR</dcterms:type>
    <dcterms:type xml:lang="it">Strumento di valutazione FAIR</dcterms:type>
    <dcterms:type xml:lang="pt">Ferramenta de avaliação FAIR</dcterms:type>
    <dcterms:type xml:lang="ro">Instrument de evaluare FAIR</dcterms:type>
    <dcterms:type xml:lang="no">FAIR-evalueringsverktøy</dcterms:type>
    <dcterms:type xml:lang="el">Εργαλείο αξιολόγησης FAIR</dcterms:type>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://services.agroportal.lirmm.fr/ofaire/"/>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://catalogue.fair-impact.eu/resources/ofaire"/>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://github.com/agroportal/fairness"/>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://fair-impact.eu/fair-assessment-tools"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#OBSEA">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site"/>
    <dcterms:spatial rdf:resource="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vilanova_i_la_Geltrú"/>
    <OSO:containsPlatform rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#OBSEA_buoy"/>
    <OSO:containsPlatform rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#OBSEA_seabed_station"/>
    <OSO:hasCountry rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Spain"/>
    <OSO:hasSiteResponsible rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Joaquin_DEL_RIO"/>
    <OSO:isTestSite rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean">true</OSO:isTestSite>
    <skos:notation>6103565</skos:notation>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="en">OBSEA is a cabled seafloor observatory located 4 km off the Vilanova i la Geltrú coast in a fishing protected area. It is connected to the coast by an energy and communications mixed cable (OceanOPS WMO number: 6103565).</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="ca">OBSEA és un observatori submarí cablejat situat a 4 km de la costa de Vilanova i la Geltrú dins d’una àrea protegida de pesca. Està connectat a terra mitjançant un cable mixt d’energia i comunicacions (OceanOPS WMO número: 6103565).</dcterms:description>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Cabled seafloor observatory located offshore Vilanova i la Geltrú, connected to shore by a mixed power and communication cable.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="es">Observatorio submarino cableado situado frente a Vilanova i la Geltrú, conectado a la costa mediante un cable mixto de energía y comunicaciones.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="ca">Observatori submarí cablejat situat davant de Vilanova i la Geltrú, connectat a la costa mitjançant un cable mixt d’energia i comunicacions.</skos:definition>
    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="en">OBSEA cabled observatory</skos:altLabel>
    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="fr">Observatoire câblé OBSEA</skos:altLabel>
    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="es">Observatorio cableado OBSEA</skos:altLabel>
    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="ca">Observatori cablejat OBSEA</skos:altLabel>
