  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#eastBoundLongitude">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty"/>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#BoundingBox"/>
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#float"/>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Easternmost longitude of a geographic bounding box, corresponding to eastBoundLongitude in ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="fr">Longitude orientale maximale d’une boîte englobante géographique, correspondant à eastBoundLongitude dans l’ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">Longitud oriental máxima de una caja geográfica delimitadora, correspondiente a eastBoundLongitude en ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="it">Longitudine orientale massima di un riquadro geografico, corrispondente a eastBoundLongitude in ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="pt">Longitude oriental máxima de uma caixa geográfica delimitadora, correspondente a eastBoundLongitude na ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="no">Østligste lengdegrad i en geografisk avgrensningsboks, tilsvarende eastBoundLongitude i ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="ro">Longitudinea estică maximă a unei zone geografice delimitate, corespunzătoare eastBoundLongitude din ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">Η ανατολικότερη γεωγραφική longitude ενός γεωγραφικού πλαισίου, που αντιστοιχεί στο eastBoundLongitude του ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">east bound longitude</rdfs:label>
