    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">A community and alliance supporting the development and maintenance of OntoPortal-based semantic artefact repositories.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">Une communauté et alliance soutenant le développement et la maintenance de dépôts d’artefacts sémantiques fondés sur OntoPortal.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="es">Una comunidad y alianza que apoya el desarrollo y mantenimiento de repositorios de artefactos semánticos basados en OntoPortal.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="it">Una comunità e alleanza che sostiene lo sviluppo e la manutenzione di repository di artefatti semantici basati su OntoPortal.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="pt">Uma comunidade e aliança que apoia o desenvolvimento e a manutenção de repositórios de artefactos semânticos baseados no OntoPortal.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="ro">O comunitate și alianță care sprijină dezvoltarea și întreținerea depozitelor de artefacte semantice bazate pe OntoPortal.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="no">Et fellesskap og en allianse som støtter utvikling og vedlikehold av OntoPortal-baserte semantiske artefaktlagre.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="el">Μια κοινότητα και συμμαχία που υποστηρίζει την ανάπτυξη και τη συντήρηση αποθετηρίων σημασιολογικών τεχνουργημάτων βασισμένων στο OntoPortal.</skos:definition>
    <schema1:name>OntoPortal Alliance</schema1:name>
    <schema1:url rdf:resource="https://ontoportal.org/"/>
    <schema1:logo rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#OntoPortalLogo"/>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://ontoportal.org/"/>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://github.com/ontoportal"/>
  </rdf:Description>
