  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#isGeometryOf">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty"/>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#Geometry"/>
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Site"/>
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Subsite"/>
    <owl:inverseOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#hasGeometry"/>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Links a geometry to the site or subsite it describes.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="fr">Lie une géométrie au site ou sous-site qu’elle décrit.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">Relaciona una geometría con el sitio o subsitio que describe.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="it">Collega una geometria al sito o sottosito che descrive.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="pt">Liga uma geometria ao local ou sublocal que descreve.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="no">Knytter en geometri til stedet eller underområdet den beskriver.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="ro">Leagă o geometrie de situl sau subsitul pe care îl descrie.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">Συνδέει μια γεωμετρία με την τοποθεσία ή υποτοποθεσία που περιγράφει.</rdfs:comment>
