  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#isManagedBy">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty"/>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ERIC"/>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ResearchInfrastructure"/>
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Organization"/>
    <owl:inverseOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#managesInfrastructure"/>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Links a research infrastructure (ERIC or national) to the organisation that manages or coordinates it.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="fr">Lie une infrastructure de recherche (ERIC ou nationale) à l’organisation qui la gère ou la coordonne.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">Relaciona una infraestructura de investigación (ERIC o nacional) con la organización que la gestiona o coordina.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="it">Collega un'infrastruttura di ricerca (ERIC o nazionale) all'organizzazione che la gestisce o coordina.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="pt">Liga uma infraestrutura de investigação (ERIC ou nacional) à organização que a gere ou coordena.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="no">Knytter en forskningsinfrastruktur (ERIC eller nasjonal) til organisasjonen som administrerer eller koordinerer den.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="ro">Leagă o infrastructură de cercetare (ERIC sau națională) de organizația care o gestionează sau coordonează.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">Συνδέει μια ερευνητική υποδομή (ERIC ή εθνική) με τον οργανισμό που τη διαχειρίζεται ή τη συντονίζει.</rdfs:comment>
