  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#hasBoundingBox">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty"/>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility"/>
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#BoundingBox"/>
    <owl:inverseOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#isBoundingBoxOf"/>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Links a Regional Facility to its spatial extent, aligned with EX_Extent/EX_GeographicBoundingBox in ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="fr">Lie une infrastructure régionale à son emprise spatiale, alignée sur EX_Extent/EX_GeographicBoundingBox dans ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">Relaciona una infraestructura regional con su extensión espacial, alineada con EX_Extent/EX_GeographicBoundingBox en ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="it">Collega una infrastruttura regionale alla sua estensione spaziale, allineata con EX_Extent/EX_GeographicBoundingBox in ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="pt">Liga uma infraestrutura regional à sua extensão espacial, alinhada com EX_Extent/EX_GeographicBoundingBox na ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="no">Knytter en regional infrastruktur til dens geografiske utstrekning, i samsvar med EX_Extent/EX_GeographicBoundingBox i ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="ro">Leagă o infrastructură regională de extinderea sa spațială, aliniată cu EX_Extent/EX_GeographicBoundingBox din ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">Συνδέει μια περιφερειακή υποδομή με τη χωρική της έκταση, ευθυγραμμισμένη με το EX_Extent/EX_GeographicBoundingBox του ISO 19115-3.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has bounding box</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="fr">a une boîte englobante</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="es">tiene caja envolvente</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="it">ha un riquadro di delimitazione</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="pt">tem caixa delimitadora</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="no">har avgrensningsboks</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="ro">are bounding box</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="el">έχει οριοθετημένο πλαίσιο</rdfs:label>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">has bounding box</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="fr">a une boîte englobante</skos:prefLabel>
