    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">A subsite of the Lucky Strike hydrothermal observatory within EMSO-Azores, associated with autonomous ocean observing devices and notable for its distinctive hydrothermal fluid chemistry.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">Un sous-site de l’observatoire hydrothermal Lucky Strike au sein d’EMSO-Açores, associé à des dispositifs d’observation autonomes et remarquable par la composition particulière de ses fluides hydrothermaux.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="pt">Um subsite do observatório hidrotermal Lucky Strike no âmbito do EMSO-Açores, associado a dispositivos autónomos de observação e caracterizado pela composição particular dos seus fluidos hidrotermais.</skos:definition>
    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="en">Capelinhos subsite</skos:altLabel>
    <skos:altLabel xml:lang="en">Capelinhos autonomous devices area</skos:altLabel>
