    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">A planned marine observatory site offshore Portugal, intended to expand IbMa-related EMSO observation activities.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="fr">Un site d’observatoire marin planifié au large du Portugal, destiné à étendre les activités d’observation EMSO liées à IbMa.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="pt">Um local de observatório marinho planeado ao largo de Portugal, destinado a expandir as atividades de observação EMSO relacionadas com o IbMa.</skos:definition>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="en">Planned marine observatory site, not yet deployed and currently without associated platforms.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="fr">Site d’observatoire marin planifié, non encore déployé et ne disposant pas encore de plateformes associées.</dcterms:description>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="pt">Local de observatório marinho planeado, ainda não implantado e sem plataformas associadas.</dcterms:description>
    <skos:note xml:lang="en">The first deployment date is provisional and corresponds to the currently planned deployment date.</skos:note>
    <skos:note xml:lang="fr">La date de premier déploiement est prévisionnelle et correspond à la date actuellement planifiée.</skos:note>
    <skos:note xml:lang="pt">A data da primeira implantação é provisória e corresponde à data atualmente planeada.</skos:note>
  </rdf:Description>
